headline: Hilton: The Rise of Dual-Brand Hotels;With more than 100 dual-brand properties under development, pairings like Hilton's Home2 Suites by Hilton and Tru by Hilton dual-brand are delivering flexibility
summary: Hilton - One hotel. One big sign above the door letting you know which brand it belongs to. That was the status quo for hotels - at least, until the early 2000s, when dual-brand hotels first arrived...
